OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show could lose over #1m
OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,FThe Royal Welsh Show and the National
OL,7,FEisteddfod have today joined forces to
OL,8,Foppose school term reorganisation
OL,9,Fplans, which could see pupils in class
OL,10,Fduring the first week of the
OL,11,Ftraditional school summer holidays.
OL,13,FThat would coincide with the annual
OL,14,FRoyal Welsh Show, which is the largest
OL,15,Fagricultural show of its kind in
OL,16,FEurope and takes place at Llanelwedd
OL,17,Fevery year.
