OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show could lose over #1m
OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,FShow organisers say that if pupils and
OL,7,Ftheir families did not attend the
OL,8,Fevent because they were in school, the
OL,9,Fsociety "could lose more than one
OL,10,Fmillion pounds" due to "reduced gate
OL,11,Fsales, membership and camping revenue".
OL,13,FBut in years gone by, the Royal Welsh
OL,14,Fwould sometimes coincide with the end
OL,15,Fof the school year, so why should the
OL,16,Fsociety need to worry now?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
