OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show could lose over #1m
OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,F"Then it was a temporary situation
OL,7,Fwhich affected some counties, some of
OL,8,Fthe time," said the chief executive of
OL,9,Fthe Royal Welsh Agricultural Society,
OL,10,FAled Rhys Jones.
OL,12,FHe said: "This would be a permanent
OL,13,Fsituation affecting everybody. And we
OL,14,Fwant all the children and teachers in
OL,15,FWales to have the ability to attend
OL,16,Fthe Royal Welsh Show legally. We see
OL,17,Fourselves as partners in education.
OL,19,F"We provide extracurricular activities
OL,20,Ffor young people that come to the
OL,21,Fshow."
