OL,6,F"In fact, all the evidence suggests to
OL,7,Fthe contrary, and in other countries
OL,8,Faround the world that have longer
OL,9,Fsummer holidays, pupils actually do
OL,10,Fmuch better than we do in Wales."
OL,12,FHowever the debate centres around
OL,13,Fseveral issues. Some argue that
OL,14,Fparents struggle to find childcare for
OL,15,Fthe length of the summer holidays.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
