OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show could lose over #1m
OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,FOthers say that disadvantaged pupils
OL,7,Fmay be going without a hot meal every
OL,8,Fday for six weeks, and there are
OL,9,Fsuggestions that pupils and teachers
OL,10,Fbecome very tired by Christmas after
OL,11,Fbeing in school from the start of
OL,12,FSeptember for the long autumn term.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government said: "This is an
OL,15,Fopportunity to design a school
OL,16,Fcalendar that works better for
OL,17,Flearners, teachers and staff, and
OL,18,Fgives everyone the best chance to
OL,19,Fthrive in school.
