OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,F"We continue to engage with key
OL,7,Fstakeholders, like the Royal Welsh
OL,8,FShow, and the public consultation
OL,9,Foffers everyone the opportunity to
OL,10,Fhave their voice heard on the
OL,11,Fproposals."
OL,13,FBut some teachers feel differently.
OL,14,FNia Rees works at a West Wales school,
OL,15,Fher family go to the Royal Welsh Show
OL,16,Ffor their annual holiday.
OL,18,FHer three children compete in
OL,19,Fcompetitions, and her husband has
OL,20,Ftrade stands at the event for the week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
