OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show could lose over #1m
OL,4,Cahead of school term changes
OL,6,FIf the Royal Welsh Show clashed with
OL,7,Fthe end of the school academic year in
OL,8,F2026, she and her family would no
OL,9,Flonger be able to go.
OL,11,FNia said: "We go to support my
OL,12,Fchildren and my husband.
OL,14,F"We stay up there, we enjoy, and if
OL,15,Fthese changes came in and I was
OL,16,Fworking in a school, I wouldn't be
OL,17,Fable to go. We wouldn't be able to
OL,18,Fcontinue with the tradition that we
OL,19,Fusually do. And the children would be
OL,20,Fabsolutely devastated."
