OL,6,FYoung people would "miss out" on the
OL,7,Fchance to "socialise and compete at
OL,8,Fthe Royal Welsh Show" if they are "in
OL,9,Fclass", says Mared Rand Jones, chief
OL,10,Fexecutive of the Wales Young Farmers
OL,11,Forganisation. She also fears it could
OL,12,Fhave an "impact on their mental
OL,13,Fhealth".
OL,15,FShe said: "It's good for their health
OL,16,Fand wellbeing for young farmers to get
OL,17,Ftogether and network.
