OL,6,F"We had a meeting with our members at
OL,7,Fcouncil last weekend, and they were
OL,8,Fall very concerned about this. It's
OL,9,Fthe pinnacle of our year and we would
OL,10,Fface real consequences if these
OL,11,Fproposals were to come to fruition."
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government says it has an
OL,14,Fongoing consultation for everybody to
OL,15,Fbe able to participate which will run
OL,16,Funtil 12 February 2024.
